snippet.title: Hunchback II: Quasimodo's Revenge C64 Longplay [65] Full Playthrough / Walkthrough #c64 #retrogaming
snippet.description:
Longplay /complete playthrough of the C64 classic Hunchback 2: Quasimodo's Revenge in which Quasimodo is tasked with rescuing Esmerelda once more. Published 9 March 2018.

Hunchback  I longplay: https://youtu.be/xYzLbW_tZz0

Hunchback II is longplay No. 190 of the Ludophiles longplays project:
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLFXG3BI19O5rpA9sB1_-K_x5s207hoahb
- http://www.ludophiles.com/threads/ludophiles-longplays-project.180/

Hunchback II: Quasimodo's Revenge is longplay No. 65 of RecordedC64Games.org:
- https://recordedc64games.org/hunchback-ii-quasimodos-revenge/
